Video 9 — if-else and elif

Overview:
Build multi-branch decisions with if-elif-else. Handles multiple scenarios efficiently.

Key Concepts:

elif for intermediate conditions
else as a default fallback

Example:

if score >= 90:
    grade = "A"
elif score >= 80:
    grade = "B"
else:
    grade = "C"

Practical Insights:

Prevents deeply nested conditions
Makes code readable and maintainable
